data.value:
1. Click the Generate Client Key to generate an activation key. Remember the path/location of the key you have generated.
2. Send the generated client key to Intellismart through email.
3. You will receive an Activation Application that you need to run once for product registration.
4. Once the you have run the Activation Application, you can now login to Giraffe.
